{"tid":2103659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不只F-35 日本還要在2031年建造第6代戰鬥機","createTime":"2020-07-11T11:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T09:45:22.000Z","uid":75656,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f318b7aafc3d63769c329cf197429677d5ceee29","tid":2103659,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"綜合媒體報導，日本防衛大臣河野太郎本週向國會報告，日本的第六代戰鬥機「F-X」將在2031財政年開始製造，要取代以美製F-16為原型改造的第四代單引擎戰鬥機F-2機隊，數量近100架。<br />\n<br />\n據日本防衛省防衛裝備廳所說明的「F-X」規格特色，包括整合射擊控制系統，可在友機鎖定目標的情況下同步以飛彈瞄準；與F-22類似的內埋武器艙以及向量噴嘴，能讓戰鬥機的動作變得更加銳利。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，日本2020年的財政預算已為研製計畫撥出2.61億美元（約新台幣77.9億元），當中還包括發展可配合匿蹤戰機行動的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3224928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224928&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyDmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=ae1bcde0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224928&h=e9b87f1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3224928</a>"},{"pid":"4047979d8e7f27231b9dbc377fe128bcd799584e","tid":2103659,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"美國批准？"},{"pid":"243c01f5b736f296658127b900bf5f1c5fe946f1","tid":2103659,"uid":605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"Macross?"},{"pid":"2b1b528d3d66cfb741082899ce0b21aa6da3197f","tid":2103659,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"哂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十式戰車咁高成本仲唔夠 仲要玩埋飛機"},{"pid":"a45615278a493fc1b9c49eef19fa914554eea174","tid":2103659,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1b528d3d66cfb741082899ce0b21aa6da3197f","tid":2103659,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:24:58.000